title: Pak Women Cricket Team Reaches in West Indies
text:
Cricket , News Â· Tagged: Cricket , Doha , Lahore , Pakistan women cricket team , t20 , West Indies 

  matches against West Indies women cricket team. 
Pak women cricket team has to travel to the long distance as they reached Doha from Lahore and they stayed there for some time. Then they set off to Miami, city of American state, Florida and they stayed there for one day. Then Pakistan women cricket team reached Saint Lucia to play the series against West Indies. 
Pakistan women cricket team will play their T20 matches against West Indies on 29 th and 31 st October and the final T20 will be played on 01 st November. Then Pak women cricket team will play their one-day international matches on 16 th , 18 th , 21 st and 24 th November. Then Pak women cricket team will reach to America to play two exhibition T20 cricket matches and return to Pakistan. Advertisement
